			Profile
			
			
A.PingZhangreceivedtheB.S.andM.S.degreesfromZhejiangUniversity,China,in1997and2000,respectively,andthePh.D.degreeinElectricalEngineeringfromHongKongPolytechnicUniversityin2003.Since2005,&nbsp;heisthe&nbsp;Associate&nbsp;ProfessorofOpticalEngineering&nbsp;atZhejiangUniversity.He&nbsp;was&nbsp;aresearchscholarofSateUniversityofNewYorkat&nbsp;BuffalofromMay2006toJune2008,andUniversityofCalifornia,SanDiegofromJuly2011toJan.2012,respectively.&nbsp;Hehaspublishedmorethan70researcharticlesinwell-knownjournalsandconferences.Hiscurrentresearchinterestsincludelasernanofabricationtechnologies,opticalfibersensorsandcommunication&nbsp;devices.

			
				
